Articles.Content:
these are my space craft from my timeplaying stock ksp from my space program.

These are some of my greatest achievments in ksp as usually i play heavily modded

First up Tsoago Space Station

Modules from Left-Right

CTS(Crew Transport Ship) Sheeraian Hawk, the first expedition to the Space Station carrying Jeb, Bob and Bill

The Floo Command module, the first module of the space station

The Zodiac Lab, Carrying Sigmund Kerman.

Next my attempt at copying UKube-1 Scotlands first Satellite(It's about time Scotland got to space!)

and heres the real one.

Note to moderators could someone move these to the spacecraft exchange

Mods I'm using;

Aviation Lights(only one that adds parts)

Environmental Visual Enhancements

Chatterer

Distant Object Enhancement

Enhanced Nav Ball

Improved Chase Cam

Navy Fish Docking Alignment

Soundtrack Editor

Texture Replacer

Kerbal Engineer Redux (For Info)

Taverio's Pizza and Aerospace

.Craft files;

CTS Sheeraian Hawk - http://www./download/sj7h3vwu9cqqzii/CTS+Sheeraian+Hawk.craft

The Floo CM - http://www./download/g1gn39biyqagyv5/Floo+CM.craft

The Zodiac Lab - http://www./download/i1cpwvjg6m7i5ia/Zodiac+Lab+1.craft

UKube-1 - http://www./download/r1p04tvaw4zp8xu/UKube+1.craft

P.S. Im 95% sure that all these have launchers if not all the payloads are no more than 10 tons.

The Zodiac Lab and UKube-1 require Aviation Lights.

Edited July 10, 2014 by Commander Jebidiah
This should be in the spacecraft exchange, but good work on those craft's nonetheless!
